توسيع نطاق التوصيل واضافة خدمة الشحن المبرد

- Re-evaluate the performance of your delivery partners, especially those operating in the Western Region, specifically Imail and J&T. We are receiving a high volume of customer complaints regarding delayed deliveries and unprofessional behavior from delivery drivers.

- Improve system synchronization between Starlinks and your delivery partners. We continue to face issues where shipments are already delivered, but no update is reflected in your system due to delays or failures in data synchronization.

- Address the ongoing issue of rejected deliveries for heavy-weight shipments, which has led to a noticeable increase in cancellations and returns during Q2. A clear and committed process for handling such shipments is needed.

- Enhance shipment visibility and tracking transparency on your portal. Currently, we lack critical details such as:

1-Reasons for rescheduling

2-Reasons for failed delivery attempts

3-Proof of delivery to customers
Overall, require a more seamless way of having deliveries to customers in KSA
Thank you for your services, for improvement: adding the invoices  on the system will help us a lot. Also for the last mile, reaching other cities for the Heavy and Bulky is very limited.
